                    </span>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="span2 record-cell" style="margin-left:10px;">
                <div class="record-label">&nbsp;</div>
                <span>
                    <span>
						<button class="btn btn-primary" id="btnBuscarClientesBuro" type="button" style="display:none">Buscar
